** Create a mysql database for image-dropbox **

(beyond the scope of these instructions; try http://www.phpmyadmin.net/ )

** Command line to get the repository **

$ cd (parent directory where you want image-dropbox to run)
$ git clone git@github.com:thunderrabbit/image-dropbox.git
$ cd image-dropbox
$ cp core/conf.sample core/conf.php

** Make changes to core/conf.php **

$path = '/home/username/path/to/webroot/image-dropbox/';	// actual directory where image-dropbox is hosted

$url = 'domain.tld';		// the root URL where image-dropbox will be accessed via web browser

settings for database

** Set up database tables **

do EITHER of these:

* visit install/ in web browser

     OR

* copy+paste schema.sql into PHPMyAdmin

